What if the wife is aware of the arrangement? I read on some blog few years back of a young girl who had an affair with the Pastor of a widely recognized mega assembly(she didn't mention), according to the her, the wife knew about it and was even very friendly (buying her gifts and sending money as well) she also mentioned the Pastor sponsored her family members. Seems unbelievable huh? I'm sorry to say this but I think what they do is beyond the physical. We all claim to serve one God but some of these churches that operate have laid foundation with the kingdom of darkness which must have given them conditions to successfully run their mega churches. What if this is one out of several others? Secondly, I don't think it's fair to blame the victims, remember he said some were threatened? It hurts to admit but I'm a victim of sexual molestation and trust me it was never a pleasant experience, my story is too long abeg but my point is NO VICTIM IS TO BLAME. You're free to disagree but please nobody should insult me.
